<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>raven-memory — a memory field that dreams</title>
<meta name="description" content="An adaptive memory substrate for agentic AI: Voronoi geometry, ternary computing, spectral optics, and sleep consolidation. Qwen Cloud Hackathon, Track 1: MemoryAgent.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..700;1,9..144,300..700&family=Schibsted+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&family=Spline+Sans+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ============================================================
   raven-memory — design tokens
   night #0A0D16 · membrane #141A2A · moonlight #E9ECF5
   plume #939BB0 · resonance #5EE6D0 · veridical gold #E9B94D
   inhibition ember #E2604E · spectral violet #8B7CF6
   ============================================================ */
:root{
  --night:#0A0D16;
  --night-2:#0D1120;
  --membrane:#141A2A;
  --membrane-2:#1A2236;
  --hairline:rgba(233,236,245,.08);
  --hairline-2:rgba(233,236,245,.14);
  --moonlight:#E9ECF5;
  --plume:#939BB0;
  --plume-dim:#5E6activé680;
  --resonance:#5EE6D0;
  --gold:#E9B94D;
  --ember:#E2604E;
  --violet:#8B7CF6;
  --display:'Fraunces','Noto Serif SC',Georgia,serif;
  --body:'Schibsted Grotesk',-apple-system,'PingFang SC','Hiragino Sans GB','Microsoft YaHei','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;
  --mono:'Spline Sans Mono',ui-monospace,'SF Mono',Menlo,monospace;
  --max:1180px;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--night);
  color:var(--plume);
  font-family:var(--body);
  font-size:17px;
  line-height:1.65;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
::selection{background:rgba(94,230,208,.25);color:var(--moonlight)}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:var(--display);color:var(--moonlight);font-weight:500;line-height:1.12}
a{color:var(--resonance);text-decoration:none}
button{font-family:var(--body);cursor:pointer}
.wrap{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px}
.eyebrow{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11.5px;letter-spacing:.22em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--resonance);
}
html[lang="zh"] .eyebrow{letter-spacing:.34em}
section{position:relative;padding:110px 0}
.sec-head{max-width:680px;margin-bottom:56px}
.sec-head h2{font-size:clamp(30px,4.4vw,46px);margin:14px 0 18px}
.sec-head p{font-size:18px}

/* ---- nav ---- */
nav{
  position:fixed;inset:0 0 auto 0;z-index:50;
  backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  background:linear-gradient(rgba(10,13,22,.82),rgba(10,13,22,.55));
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--hairline);
}
.nav-in{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;height:62px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;color:var(--moonlight);font-family:var(--display);font-size:19px;font-style:italic}
.logo svg{display:block}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:26px;margin-left:auto}
.nav-links a{color:var(--plume);font-size:14.5px;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--moonlight)}
#langToggle{
  display:flex;border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;
  background:rgba(20,26,42,.6);
}
#langToggle button{
  background:none;border:0;color:var(--plume);font-size:13px;padding:7px 14px;
  font-family:var(--mono);transition:all .2s;
}
#langToggle button.active{background:var(--resonance);color:#06251F;font-weight:500}
#langToggle button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--resonance);outline-offset:-2px}

/* ---- hero ---- */
header{position:relative;height:100svh;min-height:640px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;overflow:hidden}
#heroField{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%}
.hero-veil{
  position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(120% 90% at 18% 88%, rgba(10,13,22,.88) 0%, rgba(10,13,22,.45) 42%, transparent 70%),
    linear-gradient(rgba(10,13,22,.35), transparent 30%, transparent 60%, rgba(10,13,22,.85));
}
.hero-in{position:relative;z-index:2;width:100%;padding-bottom:9vh}
.hero-in .eyebrow{display:block;margin-bottom:22px}
h1{font-size:clamp(44px,7.2vw,92px);font-weight:380;letter-spacing:-.012em;max-width:13ch}
h1 em{font-style:italic;font-weight:430;
  background:linear-gradient(96deg,var(--violet) 0%,var(--resonance) 48%,var(--gold) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;
}
html[lang="zh"] h1{font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.01em;max-width:15ch}
.hero-sub{max-width:560px;font-size:19px;margin:26px 0 38px;color:var(--plume)}
.hero-cta{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;border-radius:999px;
  padding:14px 26px;font-size:15.5px;font-weight:500;border:1px solid transparent;
  transition:transform .18s,box-shadow .18s,background .18s;
}
.btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.btn-gold{background:var(--gold);color:#241A05}
.btn-gold:hover{box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(233,185,77,.18)}
.btn-ghost{border-color:var(--hairline-2);color:var(--moonlight);background:rgba(20,26,42,.4)}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--resonance);color:var(--resonance)}
.hero-hud{
  position:absolute;right:30px;bottom:30px;z-index:2;
  display:flex;gap:22px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;
  color:var(--plume);background:rgba(13,17,32,.55);border:1px solid var(--hairline);
  padding:12px 18px;border-radius:12px;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
}
.hero-hud b{display:block;color:var(--moonlight);font-size:16px;font-weight:500}
.hud-mss b{color:var(--gold)}

/* ---- legend chips ---- */
.legend{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:30px}
.chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;font-family:var(--mono);
  border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:999px;padding:6px 13px;color:var(--plume)}
.dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%}
.dot.g{background:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(233,185,77,.8)}
.dot.n{background:#3A4663}
.dot.f{background:#1C2336;border:1px solid var(--hairline-2)}
.dot.r{background:var(--ember);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(226,96,78,.7)}
.dot.c{background:var(--resonance);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(94,230,208,.7)}

/* ---- problem section ---- */
.compare{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:26px;margin-top:18px}
.compare .panel{border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:18px;padding:34px;background:var(--night-2)}
.panel h3{font-size:23px;margin-bottom:14px}
.panel.flat h3{color:var(--plume)}
.panel.field-p{border-color:rgba(94,230,208,.28);
  background:linear-gradient(165deg,rgba(94,230,208,.06),rgba(139,124,246,.05) 60%,var(--night-2))}
.panel ul{list-style:none;margin-top:16px}
.panel li{padding:8px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--hairline);font-size:15.5px}
.panel li::before{content:"— ";color:var(--plume-dim)}
.panel.field-p li::before{content:"◆ ";color:var(--resonance);font-size:11px}

/* ---- triptych ---- */
#physics{background:linear-gradient(var(--night),var(--night-2) 30%,var(--night))}
.trip{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}
.card{
  border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:18px;padding:32px 28px;background:var(--membrane);
  transition:transform .25s,border-color .25s;
}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--hairline-2)}
.card .glyph{height:118px;margin-bottom:22px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.card h3{font-size:21px;margin-bottom:11px}
.card p{font-size:15.5px}
.card .tags{margin-top:18px;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--resonance);border:1px solid rgba(94,230,208,.3);
  border-radius:6px;padding:3px 8px}
.card.gold .tag{color:var(--gold);border-color:rgba(233,185,77,.35)}
.card.violet .tag{color:var(--violet);border-color:rgba(139,124,246,.4)}

/* ---- playground ---- */
#playground{padding-top:90px}
.pg{border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--night-2);
  box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.pg-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--hairline);
  background:rgba(20,26,42,.5)}
.pg-bar .spacer{flex:1}
.pbtn{
  border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);background:var(--membrane);color:var(--moonlight);
  font-size:13.5px;padding:9px 16px;border-radius:9px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
  transition:border-color .15s,background .15s;
}
.pbtn:hover{border-color:var(--resonance)}
.pbtn:disabled{opacity:.4;cursor:default}
.pbtn .k{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%}
.pbtn.play{background:var(--gold);color:#241A05;border-color:transparent;font-weight:600}
.pbtn.play:hover{box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(233,185,77,.16)}
.pg-body{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;min-height:520px}
.pg-canvas-wrap{position:relative}
#fieldCanvas{display:block;width:100%;height:100%;min-height:520px;cursor:crosshair}
.caption{
  position:absolute;left:18px;right:18px;bottom:16px;
  background:rgba(10,13,22,.82);border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);border-radius:12px;
  padding:13px 18px;font-size:15px;color:var(--moonlight);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
  opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);transition:opacity .35s,transform .35s;pointer-events:none;
}
.caption.show{opacity:1;transform:none}
.caption .step{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:.18em;display:block;margin-bottom:3px}
.pg-side{border-left:1px solid var(--hairline);padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;background:var(--night)}
.pg-side h4{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--plume);font-weight:500}
.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.stat{border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px}
.stat b{display:block;font-size:20px;color:var(--moonlight);font-weight:500;font-family:var(--mono)}
.stat span{font-size:11.5px}
.stat.mss b{color:var(--gold)}
#results{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;min-height:120px}
.res{font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.res .bar{height:7px;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--violet),var(--resonance));min-width:3px}
.res.rf .bar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),#F4D488)}
.res .lbl{white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;color:var(--moonlight);flex:1}
.res .sc{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11.5px;color:var(--plume)}
.res.silenced{opacity:.45}
.res.silenced .bar{background:var(--ember);height:2px}
.res.silenced .lbl{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--plume)}
#emptyRes{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--plume-dim)}
.hint{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--plume-dim);border-top:1px solid var(--hairline);padding-top:14px;margin-top:auto}

/* ---- dream ---- */
#dream .flow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0;margin-top:30px;position:relative}
.fstep{padding:26px 22px;border:1px solid var(--hairline);background:var(--membrane);position:relative}
.fstep:first-child{border-radius:16px 0 0 16px}
.fstep:last-child{border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;border-left:0;
  background:linear-gradient(150deg,rgba(233,185,77,.1),var(--membrane) 55%)}
.fstep+.fstep{border-left:0}
.fstep .fnum{font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--violet);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.15em}
.fstep:last-child .fnum{color:var(--gold)}
.fstep h3{font-size:17px;margin:8px 0 8px}
.fstep p{font-size:14px}
.fstep::after{
  content:"→";position:absolute;right:-10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);
  z-index:2;color:var(--resonance);font-size:18px;background:var(--night);border-radius:50%;
  width:22px;height:22px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.fstep:last-child::after{display:none}
.dream-note{margin-top:26px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);padding:6px 0 6px 20px;font-size:16px;max-width:720px}
.dream-note em{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;font-family:var(--display)}

/* ---- audit ---- */
#audit{background:var(--night-2)}
.chain-wrap{margin-top:8px}
.chain{display:flex;gap:0;overflow-x:auto;padding:26px 4px}
.block{
  min-width:172px;border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);border-radius:13px;padding:15px 16px;
  background:var(--membrane);position:relative;margin-right:34px;flex-shrink:0;
  transition:border-color .3s,box-shadow .3s;cursor:pointer;
}
.block::after{
  content:"";position:absolute;right:-34px;top:50%;width:34px;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--resonance),rgba(94,230,208,.25));
}
.block:last-child::after{display:none}
.block .op{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.13em;color:var(--resonance);text-transform:uppercase}
.block .h{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;color:var(--moonlight);margin-top:7px;word-break:break-all}
.block .ph{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10.5px;color:var(--plume-dim);margin-top:5px;word-break:break-all}
.block.ok{border-color:rgba(94,230,208,.4)}
.block.bad{border-color:var(--ember);box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(226,96,78,.25)}
.block.bad .op{color:var(--ember)}
.block.bad::after{background:var(--ember)}
.block.tampered{border-style:dashed;border-color:var(--ember)}
.chain-controls{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
#chainVerdict{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:9px;border:1px solid var(--hairline)}
#chainVerdict.ok{color:var(--resonance);border-color:rgba(94,230,208,.4)}
#chainVerdict.bad{color:var(--ember);border-color:rgba(226,96,78,.5)}
.audit-cols{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:44px}
.acard{border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;background:var(--night)}
.acard h3{font-size:19px;margin-bottom:10px}
.acard p{font-size:15px}
.acard code{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);background:rgba(233,185,77,.08);
  padding:2px 7px;border-radius:5px}

/* ---- numbers / stack ---- */
.numbers{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:22px;margin-top:14px}
.num{border-top:1px solid var(--hairline-2);padding-top:18px}
.num b{font-family:var(--display);font-size:46px;font-weight:430;color:var(--moonlight);display:block;line-height:1}
.num b i{font-style:normal;font-size:24px;color:var(--plume)}
.num.gold b{color:var(--gold)}
.num.cy b{color:var(--resonance)}
.num span{font-size:14px;display:block;margin-top:8px}
.stack{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:44px}
.sbadge{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;border:1px solid var(--hairline-2);border-radius:9px;
  padding:9px 15px;color:var(--moonlight);background:var(--membrane)}
.sbadge i{font-style:normal;color:var(--resonance);margin-right:7px}

/* ---- footer ---- */
footer{border-top:1px solid var(--hairline);padding:54px 0 70px;background:var(--night-2)}
.foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-start}
.foot .logo{font-size:21px}
.foot-meta{font-size:14px;text-align:right}
.foot-meta b{color:var(--moonlight);font-weight:500}

/* ---- reveal ---- */
.rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.rv.in{opacity:1;transform:none}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  html{scroll-behavior:auto}
  .rv{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}
  .card:hover{transform:none}
}
@media (max-width:980px){
  .trip{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .pg-body{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .pg-side{border-left:0;border-top:1px solid var(--hairline)}
  .compare,.audit-cols{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  #dream .flow{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .fstep:first-child{border-radius:16px 0 0 0}
  .fstep:nth-child(2){border-radius:0 16px 0 0}
  .fstep:nth-child(3){border-left:1px solid var(--hairline);border-top:0;border-radius:0 0 0 16px}
  .fstep:last-child{border-radius:0 0 16px 0;border-top:0}
  .fstep:nth-child(2)::after,.fstep:nth-child(3)::after{display:none}
  .numbers{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .hero-hud{display:none}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-in">
    <a class="logo" href="#top" aria-label="raven-memory">
      <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 19 C7 8 13 4 23 4 C19 7 18 9 17.5 11.5 L21 12 L16.5 13.5 C15 18 10 21 3 19 Z" fill="#E9ECF5"/>
        <circle cx="18.2" cy="7.6" r="1" fill="#0A0D16"/>
      </svg>
      raven-memory
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#problem" data-i18n="nav.field">The field</a>
      <a href="#playground" data-i18n="nav.play">Playground</a>
      <a href="#dream" data-i18n="nav.dream">Dreaming</a>
      <a href="#audit" data-i18n="nav.audit">Audit chain</a>
      <a href="#stack" data-i18n="nav.stack">Stack</a>
    </div>
    <div id="langToggle" role="group" aria-label="Language">
      <button id="btnEn" class="active" aria-pressed="true">EN</button>
      <button id="btnZh" aria-pressed="false">中文</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<header id="top">
  <canvas id="heroField" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div class="hero-veil"></div>
  <div class="wrap hero-in">
    <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n="hero.eyebrow">Qwen Cloud Hackathon · Track 1 — MemoryAgent</span>
    <h1 data-i18n-html="hero.title">Memory is a <em>field</em>,<br>not a lookup table.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub" data-i18n="hero.sub">raven-memory gives AI agents a living memory substrate: Voronoi geometry, ternary logic, spectral optics — with synapses that learn, contradictions that inhibit, and nights in which it dreams.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-gold" href="#playground" data-i18n="hero.cta1">Play with the field</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#problem" data-i18n="hero.cta2">Read the architecture</a>
    </div>
    <div class="legend">
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot g"></span><span data-i18n="legend.r">REINFORCED — validated truth</span></span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot n"></span><span data-i18n="legend.n">NEUTRAL — open hypothesis</span></span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot f"></span><span data-i18n="legend.f">FORGOTTEN — silenced</span></span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot r"></span><span data-i18n="legend.i">inhibitory link</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-hud" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hud-mss"><b id="hudMss">—</b><span data-i18n="hud.mss">stability (MSS)</span></div>
    <div><b id="hudCells">—</b><span data-i18n="hud.cells">cells</span></div>
    <div><b id="hudLinks">—</b><span data-i18n="hud.links">inhibitory</span></div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ============ PROBLEM ============ -->
<section id="problem">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head rv">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n="prob.eyebrow">Why a field</span>
      <h2 data-i18n="prob.title">Flat vector search remembers everything — and learns nothing.</h2>
      <p data-i18n="prob.sub">Most agent memory is a cosine ranking over a static index. Every memory is equally true forever; contradictions live side by side; nothing consolidates. raven-memory replaces the index with a dynamical system.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="compare rv">
      <div class="panel flat">
        <h3 data-i18n="prob.flat.t">Flat vector store</h3>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="prob.flat.1">Similarity is the only signal — no notion of validation</li>
          <li data-i18n="prob.flat.2">Contradictions are retrieved together, confidence-free</li>
          <li data-i18n="prob.flat.3">The index only grows; old noise ranks like new truth</li>
          <li data-i18n="prob.flat.4">Retrieval is stateless — recalling changes nothing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="panel field-p">
        <h3 data-i18n="prob.field.t">raven-memory field</h3>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="prob.field.1">Ternary states: REINFORCED truths outshine, FORGOTTEN noise goes dark</li>
